Tap how you would act.</p><ol><li>Leave it</li><li>Notify manager<ul><li>Correct: Any merchandise that has missed markdowns is to be highlighted to the store manager. They will review the item and price.</li><li>Any team member found intentionally holding stock aside for later purchase at a lower price will face disciplinary action and possible termination of employment.</li></ul></li></ol><p><strong>Kmart Resources</strong></p><p>Kmart relies on many resources to make sure we remain a leading retailer. These resources include stock, money, equipment, stationery, files, data, records, computer hardware and software, intellectual property and company work time.</p><p>Protecting our resources means we safeguard our competitive advantage.</p><p>Because we need to protect our resources, Kmart will not accept deliberate or reckless damage to any of our resources. We also do not tolerate theft or misuse of our property or resources. Any team member that breaches this policy may face disciplinary action and possible termination of employment.</p><p><strong><em>Summary</em></strong></p><p><strong><em>In this module you have learnt about Kmart’s Automated clearance and resources policy and what you can and can’t do as a Kmart team member.</em></strong></p>
